~ librarian_hidden_collection
Iris Bookwright: [#mysterious] This way... watch your step, the floorboards remember grudges. \n \n[#proud] Behold! The Mycological Manuscripts of the 1800s! \nThese were thought lost in the Great Spore Incident of 1894.
